replies.msg:
Ronald Koeman: &ldquo;He [Van Dijk] deserves to win the Ballon d'Or.<br />
<br />
&quot;It's usually handed to players who make or create decisive goals, but if there ever is a time to give it to a defender, it is now.&rdquo;

Origi on Klopp: &quot;He fits perfectly in the values of the club. He's someone who loves the game, is a good man, and he pushes us.&quot;<br />
<br />
Origi: &quot;The fans. They also push us, they're special. Again... we did it all together, we needed every single person and we just have to enjoy this.&quot;

